  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GCR - Refugee participation in governance</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Partner&apos;s increased accountability and refugee voices amplified</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project supports the increased participation of refugees and asylum seekers in the governance of the Greek Council for Refugees by sponsoring and accompanying 30 new members over 2 years/2 AGM participations and other engagement activities.
The objectives are to 1. increase the voice of refugees within the decisions of an organisation which works on their behalf, and 2. increase the legitimacy of the GCR by strengthening their accountability to refugees.</narrative>
  </description>
